    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏简介&amp;故事背景</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款追求美与创造美的互动视觉小说游戏，郭一遍、荆晶亮、郑天，三个（划掉）毒舌互踩（隐藏）的年轻人凭着一腔热血开始了美容医馆的创业爆笑日常。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235180/extras/80628ec57998f193a506bd743ddcff12.avif?t=1766305414\" width=920 height=430 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个名为《型神》的医馆中，他们将通过医美手术来帮助和改造客户们的形象和未来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235180/extras/6bb1f15b534aaaacef8ce84dc562721e.avif?t=1766305414\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《型神：初见》是型神三部曲中的第一部，独创地将手术模拟与视觉小说结合到了一起。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >医人不医心，尽管来到医馆治疗的客户们有着ta们人生中的烦恼，我们只负责做好医美的部分，不替客户决定ta们的人生。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235180/extras/5ad43870b96ad45556102968a568d7d6.avif?t=1766305414\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >丰富的医美手术玩法，手把手地将医美的原理和过程展现到你的面前。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235180/extras/29903da2477fcd5f2214e7f8ac15eef9.avif?t=1766305414\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >抽脂，去皱纹，乃至丰胸。那些熟悉又陌生的概念，将在这里以最真实的样子呈现给你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235180/extras/fbb99de030cd668f22c48ca1913bdb12.avif?t=1766305414\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235180/extras/f7372a6191734e4872a23e6ba4ecef3f.avif?t=1766305414\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235180/extras/5d80fbefaa758529903b7658beb00b0e.avif?t=1766305414\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>人物介绍</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235180/extras/d5f2d5f4a2f86af96f0a0b050f8c7af5.avif?t=1766305414\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235180/extras_big/d5f2d5f4a2f86af96f0a0b050f8c7af5.webp?t=1766305414 width=1560 height=973 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >郭一遍，医馆里唯一的主治医师。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >胆大心细的他，身上似乎藏着什么秘密，失去记忆的他，试图通过在《型神》找回记忆、找回自我。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拥有短暂操纵时间的超能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235180/extras/d79eaf651210e5a86a5998765a468117.avif?t=1766305414\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235180/extras_big/d79eaf651210e5a86a5998765a468117.webp?t=1766305414 width=1560 height=973 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >荆晶亮，医馆里的护士长兼护士兼老板。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了开设型神，她狠心卖了自己仅有的几间“破店面”，盘下了现在的商铺。医者仁心的她，时常为患者的人生担忧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >是个毒舌妇（小声）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235180/extras/88445c4c1da7953602cbcbc32d23de1e.avif?t=1766305414\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235180/extras_big/88445c4c1da7953602cbcbc32d23de1e.webp?t=1766305414 width=1560 height=973 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >郑天，郭一遍的小助手。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >单纯又善良的他，总是陪伴在伙伴身边，做好小助手该做的事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >似乎被自己学生时期的教授摆了一道，而郭一遍会永远站在郑天这一边。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>手术模拟+视觉小说</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全球首款医美手术模拟游戏《型神：初见》，《型神》三部曲的第一部，她将通过下面的内容向你揭开时间大幕的一角：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5w字文本，游戏时间20h左右</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30场手术，涵盖了主流的医美技术</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4场boss战，挑战你的操作、判断和专注力</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5种不同玩法的内置游戏，形象地展示了医美技术在人体内部的运作</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2男1女3个不同性格的主人公，诙谐幽默的毒舌日常间闪烁着悬疑的光泽</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6个不同背景的客户，6种不同的人生，唯一的相同就是对美的渴望，只因我们不是工具人</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还有N个只闻其声不见其人的神秘角色，揭示了《型神》的序幕才刚刚拉开</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最后，我们回到开始的问题，时间是什么？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《型神》里，时间是走过人生的记录，时间也是抹平一切的神器，时间亦是回首时那丝丝的眷恋那淡淡的无力……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方QQ群:605269289</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
